WEBVTT

00:00:01.125 --> 00:00:02.934
A few weeks ago,

00:00:02.958 --> 00:00:04.434
I sat down with my mother

00:00:04.458 --> 00:00:09.083
and told her something that I had been
keeping from her for 22 years.

00:00:10.042 --> 00:00:12.726
From the time that I was 14 years old

00:00:12.750 --> 00:00:15.184
until I was 16,

00:00:15.208 --> 00:00:16.958
I was sexually assaulted.

00:00:18.375 --> 00:00:21.458
It was scary and confusing.

00:00:22.667 --> 00:00:24.208
It was humiliating.

00:00:25.458 --> 00:00:27.476
